		<h3>Adoption App Statuses</h3>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>New</strong> - Just received and needs initial scan.</li>
			<li><strong>Pending Response</strong> - Sent 1st email about our adoption process and waiting to hear back on confirming their readiness or gaining more information that was missing from app.</li>
			<li><strong>Workup</strong> - Calling references and completing final intervew.</li>
			<li><strong>Approved</strong> - Process complete and they are either meeting a dog or choosing a dog to adopt soon</li>
			<li><strong>Adopted</strong> - Signed their contract and check</li>
			<li><strong>Completed</strong> - Sent follow up email and heard back that the dog is doing well in the new home</li>
			<li><strong>Standby</strong> - Need a dog choice or aren't ready to adopt in the near future - will email us with updates</li>
			<li><strong>Withdrawn</strong> - Disappeared or adopted elsewhere</li>
			<li><strong>Denied</strong> - Cannot adopt</li>
			<li><strong>All</strong> - Every application</li>
			<li><strong>Active</strong> - Applications that are New, Pending Response, Workup or Approved</li>
 		</ul>

	
